<h3 data-start="5658" data-end="5680">Penjelasan diagram</h3>
<ul data-start="5681" data-end="6136">
<li data-start="5681" data-end="5744">
<p data-start="5683" data-end="5744"><strong data-start="5683" data-end="5693">Client</strong> meminta via GraphQL (query/mutation/subscription).</p>
</li>
<li data-start="5745" data-end="5870">
<p data-start="5747" data-end="5870"><strong data-start="5747" data-end="5766">GraphQL Gateway</strong> mem-parsing query, memetakan field ke resolvers yang memanggil microservices internal via REST/gRPC/db.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="5871" data-end="5956">
<p data-start="5873" data-end="5956">Hasil dikompilasikan oleh gateway dan dikirim balik ke client sebagai satu respons.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="5957" data-end="6136">
<p data-start="5959" data-end="6136">Untuk event-driven updates, services publish ke message bus (Kafka)  GraphQL dapat mendukung <strong data-start="6053" data-end="6070">subscriptions</strong> dengan meng-subscribe event bus dan push ke client via WebSocket.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="6138" data-end="6141">
<h1 data-start="6143" data-end="6227">3  Streaming replication PostgreSQL dengan Docker / Docker Compose (step-by-step)</h1>
<p data-start="6229" data-end="6244">Saya berikan:</p>
<ul data-start="6245" data-end="6479">
<li data-start="6245" data-end="6289">
<p data-start="6247" data-end="6289"><code data-start="6247" data-end="6267">docker-compose.yml</code> (primary + replica)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="6290" data-end="6349">
<p data-start="6292" data-end="6349">skrip inisialisasi <code data-start="6311" data-end="6328">init-primary.sh</code>, <code data-start="6330" data-end="6347">init-replica.sh</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="6350" data-end="6415">
<p data-start="6352" data-end="6415">contoh <code data-start="6359" data-end="6376">postgresql.conf</code> / <code data-start="6379" data-end="6392">pg_hba.conf</code> override (sederhana)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="6416" data-end="6450">
<p data-start="6418" data-end="6450">perintah run &amp; verifikasi sync</p>
</li>
<li data-start="6451" data-end="6479">
<p data-start="6453" data-end="6479">cara mempromosikan replica</p>
</li>
</ul>
<blockquote data-start="6481" data-end="6716">
<p data-start="6483" data-end="6716">Catatan praktis: contoh ini dimaksudkan untuk <strong data-start="6529" data-end="6557">belajar/eksperimen lokal</strong>. Untuk production gunakan solusi matang (Patroni, repmgr, pgpool-II, backup strategi, TLS, user credentials safety, persistent volumes di storage yang andal).</p>
</blockquote>
