<hr data-start="14132" data-end="14135">
<h2 data-start="14137" data-end="14170">Penjelasan sinkronisasi &amp; opsi</h2>
<ul data-start="14171" data-end="15048">
<li data-start="14171" data-end="14347">
<p data-start="14173" data-end="14347"><strong data-start="14173" data-end="14198">Streaming replication</strong>: primary mengirim WAL (Write-Ahead Log) ke replica melalui koneksi repl (pg_wal). Replica menerima wal stream dan apply sehingga data ter-replicate.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="14348" data-end="14859">
<p data-start="14350" data-end="14382"><strong data-start="14350" data-end="14381">Synchronous vs Asynchronous</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="14385" data-end="14859">
<li data-start="14385" data-end="14591">
<p data-start="14387" data-end="14591"><em data-start="14387" data-end="14401">Asynchronous</em> (default untuk banyak setup): primary tidak menunggu konfirmasi dari replica sebelum menyelesaikan transaksi  lebih cepat, tetapi berisiko kehilangan beberapa transaksi jika primary gagal.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="14594" data-end="14743">
<p data-start="14596" data-end="14743"><em data-start="14596" data-end="14609">Synchronous</em>: primary menunggu acknowledgement dari replica sehingga memastikan transaksi terpushed ke replica  lebih aman tapi menambah latensi.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="14746" data-end="14859">
<p data-start="14748" data-end="14859">Untuk konfigurasi synchronous, set <code data-start="14783" data-end="14808">synchronous_commit = on</code> dan atur <code data-start="14818" data-end="14845">synchronous_standby_names</code> pada primary.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="14860" data-end="15048">
<p data-start="14862" data-end="14886"><strong data-start="14862" data-end="14885">Lag &amp; observability</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="14889" data-end="15048">
<li data-start="14889" data-end="14999">
<p data-start="14891" data-end="14999">Cek <code data-start="14895" data-end="14916">pg_stat_replication</code> pada primary untuk melihat <code data-start="14944" data-end="14955">write_lag</code>, <code data-start="14957" data-end="14968">flush_lag</code>, <code data-start="14970" data-end="14982">replay_lag</code> (jika tersedia).</p>
</li>
<li data-start="15002" data-end="15048">
<p data-start="15004" data-end="15048">Gunakan monitoring/alerting pada production.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="15050" data-end="15053">
<h2 data-start="15055" data-end="15078">Troubleshooting umum</h2>
<ul data-start="15079" data-end="15443">
<li data-start="15079" data-end="15213">
<p data-start="15081" data-end="15213">Jika <code data-start="15086" data-end="15101">pg_basebackup</code> gagal: pastikan <code data-start="15118" data-end="15131">pg_hba.conf</code> primary mengizinkan user replicator dari IP replica; cek password di environment.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="15214" data-end="15336">
<p data-start="15216" data-end="15336">Jika replica stuck di recovery: cek logs <code data-start="15257" data-end="15281">docker logs pg-replica</code> untuk error seperti missing timeline atau wal segment.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="15337" data-end="15443">
<p data-start="15339" data-end="15443">Jika permission error pada volume: pastikan owner <code data-start="15389" data-end="15399">postgres</code> punya akses (kadang butuh chown pada host).</p>
</li>
</ul>
